public class PhysicalColumnImpl

An implementation of the model object 'Physical Column'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Comment
  • Data Type
  • Type Name
  • Size
  • Octect Length
  • Decimal Digits
  • Radix
  • Default Value
  • Nullable
  • Position
  • Table
